opennlp.ccg.util
Class TrieMap<KeyType,DataType>

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.util.TrieMap<KeyType,DataType>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Alphabet.Feature
public class TrieMap<KeyType,DataType>
extends Object

Implements a trie with a data object at each node. Keys are assumed to be canonical, and thus checked using identity (==) rather than equality. For efficient allocation, all children can be added at once.
